name: Overthinking
description:
Tired wall. Graffiti sided. It's me. Independent. Butterfly. 
Paint. Pilox. Colorful. Number. Watch out it's still wet. 
Instructions for use. Spray. Mixed with water. Stirred. 
Then apply it to the wall. Picture at will. The image 
follows the pattern. Color composition. Rainbow color. 
One color. The paint ran out. Pilox is out. Imagination 
stuck. Smoke. Deep suction. Exhale.
Glass coffee. Cream. Milk. You. Who knows. Sugar. 
Coffee table. Television. WL. News. Newspaper. 
Infotainment. Marry again. Divorce again. Book. Poetry. 
Short story. Miss. Forget. Hot water. Bubble. Boiling. 
Pouring. Chips. Snack. Snacks. Laptops. I hope. Internet 
access.
